Marriott unit joins Pegasus HCC system . Marriott International Inc ' s Marriot Lodging division said Monday it joined Pegasus Systems Inc ' s consolidated travel agent commission , payment and reconciliation service . The service , called Hotel Clearing Corp or HCC , has more than 60 , 000 travel agent subscribers in 147 countries . Marriott ' s participation will be effective in the third quarter of 1997 . Pegasus is based in Dallas . 
